## 1. Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Version / Details |
|-------|-----------|-------------------|
| **Frontend Framework** | Next.js (App Router) | `14.2.0` with TypeScript |
| **Frontend UI** | Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui (Radix primitives) | Tailwind `3.4.1`, Radix (Dialog, Tabs, Avatar, Dropdown, Progress, Label) |
| **Animations** | Framer Motion | `^10.18.0` |
| **Charts** | Recharts | `^2.10.4` |
| **Icons** | Lucide React | `^0.312.0` |
| **Package Manager** | pnpm | (confirmed via `pnpm-lock.yaml`) |
| **Backend / API** | Python FastAPI | `0.109.0`, served by Uvicorn `0.27.0` |
| **Database** | Supabase (PostgreSQL) | `supabase==2.28.2` (Python), `@supabase/supabase-js ^2.39.0` (JS) |
| **Authentication** | Supabase Auth | `@supabase/ssr`, `@supabase/auth-helpers-nextjs` |
| **AI SDK** | Google Gemini (GenAI) | `google-genai >= 1.68.0` — model: **`gemini-2.5-flash`** |
| **PDF Parsing** | PyMuPDF (fitz) | `pymupdf==1.27.2` |
| **HTTP Client (Backend)** | httpx | `0.26.0` |
| **Rate Limiting** | slowapi | `0.1.9` |
| **Data Validation** | Pydantic | `2.5.3` |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The README still references **Claude API (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)** and an **Anthropic API key**. The actual codebase has been fully migrated to **Google Gemini 2.5 Flash**. The README is outdated on this point.

> [!NOTE]
> No LangChain, Vercel AI SDK, or other orchestration framework is used. The Gemini integration is **direct** — a single `google.genai.Client` call with prompt engineering, no chains or agents.

